> those fake
> 	alarm lights, and a CD input.  Also I'm planning on installing a
> bass kicker
> 	for the "Ghetto Cruiser" anybody else try this, i'm thinking of
> putting it
> 	under the main couch/backseat.  And I'm planning on installing 6x9
> speakers in
> 	the hatchback, anybody try this too?
> 	Thanks,
> 	Capt Tripps
> 
